.TH LANTERN 1 "January 2026" "git-lantern"
.SH NAME
lantern \- repository visibility toolkit
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lantern
[\fICOMMAND\fR] [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
lantern provides visibility across local and GitHub repositories.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
\fBscan\fR
Scan for git repositories and export JSON.
.TP
\fBstatus\fR
Render a status table for local repositories.
.TP
\fBgithub\fR
GitHub utilities for repos and gists.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I .env
Optional GitHub credentials (GITHUB_USER, GITHUB_TOKEN).
